snippet.title: AMBER'S STORY (2006): PERIOD PIECES & TIME CAPSULES S01E09:
snippet.description:
2006 TV MOVIE based on the true story of Amber Hagerman, the 9 year old from Arlington TX who was abducted by a stranger and found murdered 4 days later, and of the process Donna Whitson and her group, PASO went through in order to ensure the activation of The Amber Alert System. In a parallel storyline, a single mother is horrified to learn her young daughter is missing, but now, in 2002, the Amber Alert System is in place.

Please note: The criticism I deliver in my reviews is strictly about the films and movies, about actors' and actresses' portrayals of real life people going through horrible tragedies. I do not intend to offend my audience or make them think I am insulting the victims themselves. These are MOVIE REVIEWS I'm doing.
